ke dust,'\u201d (25:23). Thawban said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, describe them\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11839,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/permission-to-keep-gifts\/","url_meta":{"origin":8627,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gifts: Take gifts to keep or give away in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave me a gift and I said, \"Give it to someone poorer than me.\" The Prophet said, \"Take it and keep it or give it in charity. Whatever comes to you of this property, take it without extravagance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/01\/khula-warning-divorce\/","url_meta":{"origin":8627,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khula: Warning against initiating frivolous divorce","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a woman asks her husband for a divorce without a strong reason, the fragrance of Paradise becomes forbidden for her.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2226 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u062